            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My daughter studied pre primary classes at Vruksha Montessori school. We enrolled her during the pandemic lockdown. Despite online classes, the teachers were able to create the right learning environment and enthusiasm for the kids. The classes were planned only for 45 mins every day, so that they can get the maximum attention from the children and the child to teacher ratio was also great (8:3), so the children were always engaged. My daughter really enjoyed the learning process, which is the primary reason we enrolled her in the school.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
