          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the best schools in town, Vruksha is totally like a second home, so much  of care and love they give towards each and every child, the management and staffs are very flexible and they are attend even teeny tiny concerns from the parents, a best environment for the kids to grow.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
